    Verse: 11
Tags:
  - Simplicity
---
Voluntary simplicity involves both inner and other conditions. It means
singleness of purpose, sincerity and honesty within, as well as avoidance
of exterior clutter, of many possessions irrelevant to the chief purpose of
life.
